summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Forty-sixth Street from Fifteenth Avenue Northwest to Seventeenth Avenue Northwest main sewer in the City of Seattle, by constructing a sewer under Ordinance No. 19243, creating Local Improvement District No. 1850 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
